      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine, showroom condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is your lucky day. Drop me a message and let's get you behind the wheel!",
