    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 2011 BMW M3 Coupe featuring the legendary S65B40 naturally aspirated 4.0L V8. This high-revving masterpiece delivers a linear power band up to its 8,400 RPM redline, featuring eight individual throttle bodies and a 12.0:1 compression ratio. Mated to a lightning-fast 7-speed M-DCT dual-clutch transmission and an M Variable Differential Lock, the power delivery is seamless and visceral. This specimen is in concours condition: the factory Alpine White paint retains its deep luster, and the Novillo leather interior shows zero bolster wear. Mechanically beyond reproach, the rod bearings and throttle actuators have been addressed preventatively with documented service history. The chassis remains taut with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) providing adaptable damping rates, while the subframe and bushings show no signs of fatigue. A true collector-grade E92 with zero modifications, representing the pinnacle of BMW\u2019s atmospheric engineering.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
