    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute showroom masterpiece that is indistinguishable from new. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen a drop of rain. The exterior features a flawless Deep Obsidian Pearl finish, entirely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections, and is protected by a multi-layer ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the hand-stitched Nappa leather is supple and pristine, still carrying that distinct new-car aroma without a single crease in the bolsters. Every technological feature, from the high-fidelity surround sound system to the adaptive driver assistance suite, functions with factory precision. The engine bay is detailed to a mirror finish, documenting a life of preventative maintenance performed exclusively by master technicians using genuine parts. Included are the original window sticker, two keys, and a comprehensive binder of service records. This is not just a used car; it is a time capsule for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection.",
