      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolute showroom condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, so there isn't a single scratch or dent to be found. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for perfection on wheels, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message and come take it for a spin!",
